# MX Record (for receiving bounces/feedback):
#   Type: MX
#   Name: send
#   Data: feedback-smtp.us-east-1.amazonses.com. (Priority: 10)
#   TTL: 1 Hour
#
# DKIM Record (email authentication):
#   Type: TXT
